node.text:
Pastor Rudy Rasmus knows firsthand how it feels not to be understood. Today, he dedicates his life to helping those less fortunate feel loved and included. As the co-founder of @breadoflifehoutx, and how he works with our partner @m252_org to distribute P&G products to serve both the unsheltered and underserved communities. 

Pastor Rudy’s work is one example of how we’re stepping forward to #LeadWithLove. Watch the five-part series produced with @katiecouric.
Thank you @rudyrasmus and @breadoflifehoutx for showing us a way to #LeadWithLove!
I loved your commercial that aired during the BET awards 👏👏
@mom2cj_ I came here too right after the commercial lol. So powerful!
I loved your commercial that aired during the BET awards 👏👏
